Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.32,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.08,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Comment: 10,0:01:06.80,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP end}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.77,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is working hard\N to provide for the Ijuuin family
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and is now worthy \Nof the title of "modern woman."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, she found Tamaki, \Nnow a reporter for a newspaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.72,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At first they had a toast \Nand cheerfully chatted about many things,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.51,0:01:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but afterwards they stumbled across a UFO: \Nwas it a hallucination, a dream or real?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.58,0:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, an alien who looked \Nexactly like Shinobu was on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.96,0:01:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When she awoke with a splitting hangover, \Nshe chalked the whole thing up to a drunken illusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.91,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the very next day, the dream turned into reality \Nwhen an airship from Russia landed.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is going to get off it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a dream after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a relief!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Interview them already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.42,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The two who landed are prominent figures \Nof the exiled Russian nobility.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They are Maquis Mikhailov and his wife.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleeing the red terror \Nof the revolutionary government,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they have applied \Nfor permanent residence in Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.39,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our peace-loving country \Nis more than glad to warmly welcome both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Look at how handsome he is!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if all Russians are that good-looking. {oh you flatter me}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I can't see! Fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, \NI'll just crawl from below.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinobu's perfect double...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't push!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some respect!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, this way please, Marquis.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Second Lieutenant Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you talking about, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The marquis started studying Japanese \Nin anticipation of his arrival,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but he still doesn't understand it fully!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.03,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that he strongly resembles \Nsomeone I knew, so I called him that on a spur...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.44,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, the couple \Nis going to stay at Earl Tanukikoji's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Words came out of my mouth \Nbefore I could realize what I was doing...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Malinka?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.19,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he the spitting image of Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Marquis Mikhailov...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me, Onijima.\NWhat happened to Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was severely injured, \Nyet I didn't come to his rescue
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just left him in that Siberian blizzard!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault! \NI couldn't return the favor!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Benio.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shinobu died...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all a mere coincidence...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Malinka?"
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.43,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Marquis say "malinka" \Nthe very moment he saw me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1500)}Malinka...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1500)}Malinka...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1500)}Malinka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.27,0:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu! Are you there, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, \Ninstead of interviewing them?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Editor-in-Chief...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.97,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that Marquis Mikhailov\Nisn't really a Russian aristocrat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.00,0:05:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the spitting image \Nof Ijuuin Shinobu, my betrothed!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.92,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look Japanese by any means.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Shinobu is half-Japanese.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His traits make it hard to tell his nationality.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.69,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! So what you're saying is that your betrothed is still alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is {\i1}definitely{\i0} Shinobu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to look into \NMarquis Mikhailov's background?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A headline like "Exiled Russian Aristocrat Actually Japanese" would certainly be a scoop.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Editor-in-Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Editor-in-Chief! \NThank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today calls for a celebration! \NYou’ve earned two circles of kielbasa! {/You deserve a 10 out of 10!/A++       [double circle (indicating "very good" on a piece of school work)]; also it's spelled nijuumaru - they are two "maru's" (circles)}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.07,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and me have been waiting \Nfor Shinobu's return for a really long time. {あなたを待っていくとせぞ、思えばずいぶん長い月日だったな。}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.95,0:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With those bright, graceful hair \Nand mysterious hazel eyes of his,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.58,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,could it ever be anyone \Nother than my Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He positively can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.61,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why couldn't he recognize me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After many years of hard work, \Nthere's no sign of the feminine charm I once had.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder \Nhe didn't realize who I was.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.22,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, I besotted him \Nwith nothing but my naturally pretty face...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Makeup will save the day!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some wrinkle-reducing set \Nand white powder will do!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Now that's unusual: \NBoss is preening herself before the mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet there would be no use \Nin telling you to stop right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! No! It slipped off!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You want something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A scary tanuki monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.72,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we've lost him.{idk }
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.01,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll go to sleep for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll learn everything \Nduring the interview tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, why does Shinobu...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,refer to himself \Nas Marquis Sasha Mikhailov now?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make matters worse, \Nhe even has a wife...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.91,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that woman Larisa \Nwant from Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.38,0:08:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why did he marry her \Ndespite being already betrothed to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wrap my head around all of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.17,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is Earl Tanukikoji's mansion.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.36,0:08:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a chic place for a tanuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please inform Earl Tanukikoji.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, it's me, Tanukikoji.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! He's an actual...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You see, we'd like to interview \NMarquis Mikhailov and—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.88,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Their excellencies are tired \Nand refuse to meet any press.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now shoo, shoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheapskate!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we won't be able \Nto meet them in a proper way.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're left with no proper options...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! \NYour order is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Too easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You found out?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I beg your pardon!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, some people can be obnoxious!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a magazine reporter, Mr. Tanukikoji?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you needn't worry. \NI've just driven them away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.62,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it. For the time being, we're not ready to be seeing anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.52,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! By the way, \Nhave you made any progress in Japanese?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Marquis and I \Nhave been studying all day long.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I try reading for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.80,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water \Nmay get split in two by a stepping stone... {ep 2 04:36}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water \Nmay get split in two by a stepping stone,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will eventually turn into one again.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Marquis, your pronunciation is impeccable!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, your learning rate \Nis nothing short of stunning!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, they're keeping a close guard.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.95,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why are they \Nthat opposed to an interview.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.91,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close... Just behind that window \Nthere's the one who might very well be my Shinobu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.00,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a bride of that Marquis Mikhailov, \Nso what are you going to do about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.12,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't know all the details, the current Marquis seems to already be properly married.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.18,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to intervene now,\Nyou'll do nothing but hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to keep pushing despite that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought about what I would do next.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.08,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to convince myself that Shinobu died in Siberia.\NI kept believing he was still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.27,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So if he is indeed alive, this might just be \Nmy one and only hope to hold on to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.58,0:11:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way to overcome my regret \Nof not having confessed my love back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shinobu is still alive, \Nno matter under what name...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly forgive that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.07,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how he came to this, forgetting your betrothed to live with another woman...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.94,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unforgivable. No person \Nshould ever have to suffer through this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Editor-in-Chief, did you just...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to be serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.37,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I going to say just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it... Wasn't it...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, is something wrong, Editor-in-Chief?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong, Aoe Tousei.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I hoping to achieve \Nby hiding and running away from women?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.63,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was out of fear that women \Nwould bring chaos to my orderly and noble life?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that's so... So... So...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My! So sometimes you cry too, \NEditor-in-Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you that moved \Nby my heroic determination?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! No! No, I'm not, you hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Young Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.76,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.76,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.44,Overlap,,0,0,0,,If only we could join you... {guess}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.33,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.94,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I got his underwear!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.83,0:13:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! How cruel of them! \NI can't go out like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.49,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they sure had no mercy at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fans can be truly morbid!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, you can change into this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Do you think it suits me?\NOh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You even keep his photos \Non your desk at work?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's a Russian marquis.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A marquis?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is definitely Shinobu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never forget my rival in love, alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This look, this feel.\NHe does seem a little haggard indeed,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't be wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As an actor, \NI have an eye for these things!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really no room for mistake, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe that \NMarquis Mikhailov is Shinobu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.47,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikhailov? Where have I heard \Nthis name before...?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.69,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! \NWe should go to that park.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're holding a welcome party there!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that true, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.55,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Take me to that party, \Nwon't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.23,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't. The party is hosted by the government \Nand they won't let anyone in except those concerned.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Fine by me. \NIf that's your final decision,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't I publish \Nthis nostalgic photo of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it really is you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd make the headlines for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll take you there...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my good boy, ever so obedient!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.04,0:14:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you all today. Let’s make sure \Nwe leave a good impression on our foreign guests.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these really the only roles they had?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.03,0:15:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped—lots of other actors \Nin today's show are making do with minor roles too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing a princess \Nwould've suited me way better.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.89,0:15:37.31,Song,,0,0,0,,{no idea}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.31,0:15:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, just standing here silently \Nis such a bore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this lever does...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, you can't be pulling that...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break! Ugh...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So it was you \Nwho was behind all of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They've found us! Run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.20,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't let them escape! \NThey're the saboteurs!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.\NHurry up to Marquis!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you, Editor-in-Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, I missed you so much. \NIt's me, Benio!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember? \NI'm your betrothed!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothed?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Found her!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous! \NHow dare she come! {g}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.09,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a friend of mine, \Nso please don't try to restrain her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.26,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So my husband was your...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.81,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When he saw me, he said "Malinka."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something \NSasha would say.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Malinka is the Russian word \Nfor wild raspberry flowers.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.03,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it also has the nuance \Nof "cute petite girl." {never EVER did it mean ANYTHING other than the diminutive of Malina}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.73,0:18:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. In Russia, \Nyoung men say it to approach girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was probably why Sasha said it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall I show you the proof?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The proof?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.31,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The man on these photos \Nis not your betrothed,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.88,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but none other \Nthan my husband Sasha Mikhailov.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.68,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong...\NThe marquis is not my Shinobu after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.16,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... My Shinobu... \Ndid die on that battlefield!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.89,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When Larisa saw Shinobu, who looked exactly like her late husband, lying injured in the Siberian snow,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.36,0:19:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she took advantage of his amnesia \Nand started referring to him as her husband.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.50,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Storms come with flowers, and when the storm finally subsides, the malinka flower will surely bloom.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.54,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For everyone in Taisho romance,\Na day will come when they will finally smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday flowers will bloom for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.26,0:22:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.09,0:22:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your High Collar Lady will stay forever and ever with you, in your heart.
Comment: 10,0:22:59.38,0:22:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:04.73,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:18.44,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:27.26,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:30.13,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:35.64,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
